<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<TestCaseEntity>
   <description>TC_DD_001 PIM Dropdown Selection
Objective: Verify that 4 dropdown elements on the PIM page can be selected successfully
Steps: 
1. Admin is logged in.
2. Click PIM menu
3. Verify PIM page is displayed (Employee Information header)
4. Click Employment Status dropdown
5. Select any value (e.g., Full-Time Permanent)
6. Click Job Title dropdown
7. Select any value
8. Click Sub Unit dropdown
9. Select any value
10. Click Include dropdown
11. Select Current Employees Only (or any option)</description>
   <name>TC_DD_001</name>
   <tag>drop_down</tag>
   <comment></comment>
   <recordOption>OTHER</recordOption>
